page.title: 05KATIE'S DAY
page.content: I wake up every morning at about{7:00 and normally watch cartoons on{T.V from{7:25}to{7:30.}Then I go and get dressed,wash my face,and then go down to have my breakfast.I normally have cereal and toast with honey.Then I wash my hands and clean my teeth and I go and practice my piano and violin. After I have cleaned my shoes,I normally feed the cat.About quarter past eight I go outside and with my sister until a quater to nine and then I get ready for school.If it is sunny I walk to school,if not I go by car with my mum.I am at school until half past three.Sometimes I go to clubs after school like swimming,dancing, table-tennis,brownies and band.After the activity of the day I watch{T.V until{8:30}then sometimes I have a bath,then go to bed.Sometimes I read before I go to sleep.
